data.description: Only available at this fantastic price due to job related relocation. Located just steps away from the river and its trails, this charming home is a wonderful combination of original character and modern updates. It is light and bright throughout and boasts original hardwood floors, vintage inspired tile work, fireplace, built ins, and marble accents. The kitchen and bathrooms are thoughtfully updated. The large backyard has a paver patio and is fully fenced. This neighborhood is so walkable and is close to shops, restaurants, parks, trails, schools, and so much more! Please see supplements for a list of recent updates and improvements.
